Wi-Fi monitor / wpa supplicant / connection manager.
The purpose of this tool is to allow connecting the newly booted system
to a wifi (or maybe wired) network, preferably with as little configuration
as possible.

These tools, wimon especially, may or may not face a major rewrite soon.
Regardless, it should be reasonably usabe with its current design.

See ../../doc/wimon.txt and ../../doc/wpadhcp.txt for some unresolved
issues with wimon design.
